init_text: A woman has been dating guy after guy, but it never seems to work out. She's unaware that she's actually been dating the same guy over and over; a shapeshifter who's fallen for her, and is certain he's going to get it right this time.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He also knows that she's been going to Dr. John, who is a specialist, for her asthma.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He was going to make sure he smelled good for Karen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He walked into the office and greeted the receptionist, and then he walked into the back to get ready for his first patient.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She was wearing a beautiful dress, and she looked absolutely stunning.
